# 🏗️ System Architecture

# Smart Traffic Management System

## 📖 Overview

The Smart Traffic Management System follows a modular architecture where each component performs a specific responsibility.

---

# Architecture

Camera

↓

Vehicle Detection (OpenCV + YOLO)

↓

Flask Backend

↓

MySQL Database

↓

Traffic Signal Controller

↓

Dashboard

---

# Modules

## 1. Authentication Module

Responsibilities:

- Login
- Logout
- User Management

---

## 2. Vehicle Detection Module

Responsibilities:

- Detect Vehicles
- Count Vehicles
- Identify Vehicle Types

Technology:

- OpenCV
- YOLO

---

## 3. Signal Controller Module

Responsibilities:

- Calculate Green Signal Time
- Manage Signal Timing
- Dynamic Signal Control

---

## 4. Database Module

Responsibilities:

- Store Traffic Data
- Store Vehicle Logs
- Generate Reports

Technology:

- MySQL

---

## 5. Dashboard Module

Responsibilities:

- Live Vehicle Count
- Signal Status
- Traffic Analytics
- Historical Reports

---

